    "description": "****If you are interested in viewing this kitty, please go to VOKRA website http://www.orphankittenrescue.com/adopt and submit Adoption Application****\n\nCairo is a beautiful white and orange long haired cat. He loves to find a cozy spot to curl up but when it is time to play his favorite toy is the laser pointer. He's a bit shy to start, however, once he comes out of his shell he loves running up against your legs and chatting with you! He's best in a loving home that is a quiet place for him to relax and maybe peer out a window!",
