    "description": "Please meet Mr. Green.  Mr. Green is in fact a gray Persian x.  Heâs a very relaxed young boy.  Although heâs only about eight months old you can usually find him lounging around.  He likes to chill on just about any surface.  This is not to say that this boy doesnât like to play.  Of course he does, heâs really just a kitten. \n\nMr. Green has an old eye injury but it does not seem to affect him at all.  The white on the eye is the scar from the injury.  Mr. Green came to us from another shelter and we donât have too much information on his past.  However we have been informed that he loves other felines and canines.  We figure Mr. Green will do best in a home where he has feline and/or canine companions to play with. \n\nMr. Green is a sweet kid who like attention and snuggles.  He will be a perfect addition to any family.  Not much seems to phase Mr. Green and he adjusted to the shelter very quickly. \n\nWe are sure who ever adopts Mr. Green will be one lucky family :D",
