    "description": "I am already neutered, up to date with shots, and good with cats.\n\nBOO BOO- Coon/Polydactyl's Story...\nI am the fluffiest, sweetest little gray boy my foster mom has ever seen. As I get bigger, it looks like my eyes are going to be the same lovely gray as my fur! I love to run around and play with my brothers and sisters. My favorite toy is an acorn...I can chase it across the floors for hours, throw it up in the air and catch it, and do what I can to keep those other little rascals in my litter from stealing it away from me.I am active I will love being petted and groomed as much as possible! You can see the Siamese in me from my mom as well from my big crossed eyes!I have EXTRA TOES on my paws as well and would do well if adopted with one of my siblings!",
