    "description": "February 2015\n\nLover Alert!\n\nSylvester is the little runt of the litter with the biggest name and heart. He likes being carried around ALL of the time, or will be happy riding around in your hoodie. He has had digestive issues since birth and will need some extra TLC. He likes being spoken to while lying on his back, cuddled in the crook of your arm so he can gaze into your eyes and get tummy rubs. \n\nSylvester is 100% healthy, and current on all vaccinations. He is microchipped, and has been fixed. He is ready to start sharing his forever home with you!",
