    "description": "Valor and her siblings, Caitlyn, Fortune, Gangplank, Quinn and Vi were born after their momma Maggie was rescued from the streets. Valor is quite a striking little girl. Instead of the standard tabby stripes, Valor is covered in swirls. She has a great time playing with her siblings, and with toys. Once she gets sleepy she is usually found sound asleep in a pile wherever she was just playing. \n\nValor is 100% healthy, current on all vaccinations, micro-chipped, and has been fixed. If you want to be loved forever, and want a kitty who is adorable, full of playful antics, and has lots of affection, Valor is ready to go home with you.",
