    "description": "Sweet and adorable Macy was born on September 9, 2015 and came to us on September 12, 2015 with her 4 siblings. She has been hand raised because her mother could not be found, so she is very sweet and lovable! She is a sassy and playful little girl with the best purr machine in the world. She loves attention and gets along great with other animals (including dogs!) and would be fine with kids. Her adoption fee includes her spay. FeLV test, vaccines, and microchip. Her adoption fee is $110, but if you adopt her with one of her siblings we will discount the total adoption fee to $200. She and her siblings are looking for indoor only homes. If you're interested in adopting Macy, please contact her foster at lexie@happystraysrescue.org.",
