    "contactEmail": "meoowzresq@aol.com",
    "contactZip": "90620",
    "description": "Please meet Vegas, male Siamese Flame Point DOB: 6/4/15 \nA little about me...I was found on the streets of Las Vegas (hence the name). A very kind lady drove me from Las Vegas to MeoowzResQ in Orange County and I am now safe in a foster home. I am a bit shy at first, but friendly. I am very energetic and like to show off. I would rather play than cuddle, I like affection, but don't demand it.\nI am independent, well behaved and not a picky eater. I like cat toys and playing with my foster kitty brothers and sisters. I get along with other kitties and small dogs. \nBTW~ I enjoy stroller rides.....see attached picture!\nIf you are interested in meeting me, or have specific questions, please contact Kathy at: 714-745-8060 You can meet me Saturday from 11:00-4:00 at PetCo Buena Park at the corner of Valley View and Ball Road in Buena Park, or we can meet at a time convenient for you.",
